Adrienne Morrison https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Adrienne_Morrison 0 Mabel Adrienne Morrison (March 1, 1883 – November 20, 1940) was an American stage actress of the early 20th century. She married actor Richard Bennett, with whom she had three daughters who later would become actresses.
